---
import LayoutPublic from '../layouts/LayoutPublic.astro';
---
<LayoutPublic
  title="Guía de Tallas — Crazy Monkey Collection Noir"
  description="Guía de tallas Crazy Monkey. Corte unisex recto. Medidas en centímetros para elegir tu talla perfecta."
  canonical="https://crazymonkey.store/tallas.html"
  ogTitle="Guía de Tallas — Crazy Monkey"
  ogDescription="Guía de tallas Crazy Monkey. Corte unisex recto. Medidas en centímetros para elegir tu talla perfecta."
  showFooter={false}
>
  <style is:global>
  body{min-height:100vh}
  .hero{padding:9rem 2rem 4rem;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:1}
  .hero-eyebrow{font-size:.55rem;letter-spacing:.5em;color:var(--red);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .hero-title{font-family:'UnifrakturMaguntia',cursive;font-size:clamp(38px,7vw,80px);line-height:.95;color:var(--white);text-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(176,26,26,.35);margin-bottom:.8rem}
  .hero-sub{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(11px,1.8vw,18px);letter-spacing:.4em;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:2rem}
  .hero-divider{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:3rem}
  .hero-divider span{display:block;width:50px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--red))}
  .hero-divider span:last-child{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red),transparent)}
  .hero-divider em{font-size:.5rem;color:var(--light);letter-spacing:.3em;font-style:normal}
  .content{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem 6rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
  .section-eyebrow{font-size:.5rem;letter-spacing:.4em;color:var(--red);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.2rem}
  .tallas-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.65rem;margin-bottom:2rem}
  .tallas-table thead tr{border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a}
  .tallas-table th{font-size:.5rem;letter-spacing:.3em;color:var(--red);text-transform:uppercase;padding:.6rem .8rem;text-align:center;font-weight:400}
  .tallas-table th:first-child{text-align:left}
  .tallas-table td{padding:.7rem .8rem;border-bottom:1px solid #111;color:var(--light);text-align:center;transition:background .2s}
  .tallas-table td:first-child{color:var(--white);font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-align:left}
  .tallas-table tr:hover td{background:rgba(176,26,26,.04)}
  .tallas-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
  .measure-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--white);margin:2rem 0 .8rem}
  .measure-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .measure-item{display:flex;gap:.8rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:.6rem;line-height:1.7}
  .measure-num{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--red);min-width:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0}
  .measure-text{color:var(--light)}
  .measure-text strong{color:var(--cream)}
  .tip{background:rgba(176,26,26,.05);border-left:2px solid var(--red);padding:.8rem 1rem;margin-top:1rem;font-size:.58rem;line-height:1.9;color:var(--light)}
  .tip strong{color:var(--cream)}
  .note{font-size:.58rem;line-height:2;color:var(--light);border-top:1px solid #1a1a1a;padding-top:1.2rem;margin-top:1.5rem}
  .note strong{color:var(--cream)}
  .cta-row{display:flex;gap:1rem;margin-top:2.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .cta-link{display:inline-block;font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.3em;color:var(--black);background:var(--red);padding:.7rem 1.8rem;text-decoration:none;clip-path:polygon(8px 0%,100% 0%,calc(100% - 8px) 100%,0% 100%);transition:background .2s,transform .2s}
  .cta-link:hover{background:var(--cream);transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .cta-link.secondary{background:transparent;color:var(--light);border:1px solid #2a2a2a;clip-path:none;padding:.7rem 1.8rem}
  .cta-link.secondary:hover{color:var(--cream);border-color:var(--cream)}
  </style>

<div class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">✦ Crazy Monkey Collection Noir</p>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Guía de Tallas</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Corte Unisex Recto</p>
  <div class="hero-divider"><span></span><em>Medidas en centímetros</em><span></span></div>
</div>

<div class="content">
  <p class="section-eyebrow">✦ Camisetas — Medidas de la prenda terminada</p>

  <table class="tallas-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Talla</th>
        <th>Pecho (cm)</th>
        <th>Largo (cm)</th>
        <th>Hombros (cm)</th>
        <th>Manga (cm)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>XS</td><td>86 – 91</td><td>66</td><td>42</td><td>19</td></tr>
      <tr><td>S</td><td>91 – 96</td><td>69</td><td>44</td><td>20</td></tr>
      <tr><td>M</td><td>96 – 101</td><td>72</td><td>46</td><td>21</td></tr>
      <tr><td>L</td><td>101 – 107</td><td>74</td><td>48</td><td>22</td></tr>
      <tr><td>XL</td><td>107 – 112</td><td>77</td><td>50</td><td>23</td></tr>
      <tr><td>XXL</td><td>112 – 117</td><td>79</td><td>52</td><td>24</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p class="measure-title">Cómo tomar las medidas</p>
  <div class="measure-list">
    <div class="measure-item">
      <span class="measure-num">1</span>
      <span class="measure-text"><strong>Pecho:</strong> Alrededor de la parte más ancha, con brazos relajados. Cinta horizontal, ajustada sin apretar.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="measure-item">
      <span class="measure-num">2</span>
      <span class="measure-text"><strong>Largo:</strong> Desde el punto más alto del hombro hasta el borde inferior de la prenda.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="measure-item">
      <span class="measure-num">3</span>
      <span class="measure-text"><strong>Hombros:</strong> De costura a costura por la parte trasera.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="measure-item">
      <span class="measure-num">4</span>
      <span class="measure-text"><strong>Manga:</strong> Desde la costura del hombro hasta el borde de la manga.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tip">
    <strong>¿Entre dos tallas?</strong> Elige la más grande. El corte es recto — no entallado.
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    Medidas de la prenda terminada, no del cuerpo.<br>
    ¿Dudas? Escríbenos al <strong>+57 301 656 8222</strong> o por <strong><a href="https://wa.me/573016568222" style="color:var(--cream);text-decoration:none" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a></strong>.
  </div>

  <div class="cta-row">
    <a class="cta-link" href="/index.html">Ver Catálogo</a>
    <a class="cta-link secondary" href="/envios.html">Política de Envíos</a>
  </div>
</div>
</LayoutPublic>
